<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="be-exposed-to">be exposed to</h1>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.<strong>处于可能受伤害的境遇</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>The water companies were instructed not to expose people to polluted water any more.
自来水公司被命令不得使人们再受污染水的影响。</p><footer>人教⑤ – 1</footer></div></div>